divs: Sighting DetailsSaw the object from the car. It was low, slow moving, going east. I took some photos of it with my camera phone. It looked like it may be a blimp. It was gliding soundlessly. I lost sight of it as I pulled into my destination, as the object became obscured by trees. I tried to look online to see if there were any blimps in the area but I could not find anything.
